'''印度快運航空1344號班機空難'''發生于2020年8月7日，一架載有184名乘客及6名機組人員的[[印度快運航空|印度快運航空]][[波音737新世代#737-800|波音737-8NG]]從[[迪拜國際機場|迪拜國際機場]]飛往[[印度|印度]][[科澤科德|科澤科德]][[卡利卡特國際機場|卡利卡特國際機場]]降落時衝出跑道<ref>{{cite news |date=2020-08-07 |title=Air India Express plane with 191 from Dubai skids off Kozhikode runway, pilot killed |url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/air-india-express-aircraft-from-dubai-to-calicut-with-191-passengers-crashes-reports/story-EC7jvZELVkWi32EgT2ZOmJ.html |work=[[Hindustan_Times|Hindustan Times]] |access-date=2020-08-07 |archive-date=2020-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808083600/https://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/air-india-express-aircraft-from-dubai-to-calicut-with-191-passengers-crashes-reports/story-EC7jvZELVkWi32EgT2ZOmJ.html/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-07|title=Breaking: Air India Express Boeing 737 Crashes Whilst Landing In Kozhikode|url=https://simpleflying.com/air-india-express-boeing-737-crash/|access-date=2020-08-07|website=Simple Flying|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808083602/https://simpleflying.com/air-india-express-boeing-737-crash/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2020-08-07 |title=Air India Express Plane Skids Off Runway In Kerala With 191 On Board; Pilot Dead, Tweets MP |url=https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/air-india-express-flight-with-180-passengers-from-dubai-skids-off-runway-while-landing-at-kozhikode-2276039 |publisher=[[NDTV|NDTV]] |access-date=2020-08-07 |archive-date=2020-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808083604/https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/air-india-express-flight-with-180-passengers-from-dubai-skids-off-runway-while-landing-at-kozhikode-2276039 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。客機衝出跑道後墜入跑道前的低地，機身斷成數截<ref>{{Cite web|title=Live News: Air India Express flight from Dubai over shoots table top runway|url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/latest-daily-news-and-updates-august7/liveblog/77404349.cms|